{"tid":488254,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全港義工登記逾128萬  張建宗:令人鼓舞","createTime":"2017-12-03T13:58:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-31T02:28:51.000Z","uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f5a2e11460c58734c289940eef300c65ac12f8c9","tid":488254,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T13:58:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/03/215727_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F03%2F215727_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7b066c46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政務司司長張建宗出席義務工作發展局國際義工日嘉許禮時表示，根據社署的義工登記冊，截至今年10月，有超過128萬名義工，即是本港每6個人就有1人是義工，對此感到非常鼓舞。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗又指，政府會繼續加強與制服團體及義工組織合作，建立互助、關愛及共融社會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1080521/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1080521%2F&d=I9P2errRHAQm9SPCg6XOj%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=1b5acafe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1080521%2F&h=ad8fa2ee\" target=\"_blank\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1080521/</a>"},{"pid":"595b03cf7e9ac9bb0a3af742c46a60a3b7a27e63","tid":488254,"uid":68745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T14:02:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1410c944682cbb0b12a5f6ad84f5d3a51f899bbc","tid":488254,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T14:02:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/03/215727_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F03%2F215727_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=7b066c46&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n政務司司長張建宗出席義務工作發展局國際義工日嘉許禮時表示，根據社署的義工登記冊，截至今年10月，有超過128萬名義工，即是本港每6個人就有1人是義工，對此